05:49.982 --> 05:52.644
Hey, Clyde- Sam.

05:52.719 --> 05:56.883
<i>Hey, slow down a little bit, will ya?</i>
<i>You're makin'mejumpy.</i>

05:56.956 --> 05:59.652
What am I doin' here in-
in whenever it is?

05:59.726 --> 06:02.627
It's 1 965.
May 1 1 , to be exact.

06:02.695 --> 06:05.493
And we don't know why you're here.
What are you doin' here?

06:05.565 --> 06:07.726
Well, I came to check on you
when I heard this guy Clyde...

06:07.800 --> 06:10.234
