told me to fight against, Al.

06:16.542 --> 06:19.102
I can't change these people.

06:19.178 --> 06:21.738
Well, maybe you're not here
to change them.

06:21.814 --> 06:24.510
Look, we're gonna find out
what you're here to do,

06:24.584 --> 06:27.280
then you're gonna do it,
and then you'll be history, okay?

06:27.353 --> 06:30.447
So take it easy.
Just take it easy.

06:30.523 --> 06:33.185
I'm gonna go find out what it is
you're here to do.

06:33.259 --> 06:35.557
I'll be back as quick as I can,
all right?

06:35.628 --> 06:37.619
Now, don't lose it.

06:44.971 --> 06:47.940
<i>[ Sam Narrating ]</i>
<i>In all my leaps, I don't think</i>
<i>I had ever felt more confused...</i>

06:48.007 --> 06:50.475
<i>by the people I had leapt into.</i>

06:50.543 --> 06:53.979
<i>There was part of me that liked</i>
<i>Gene and Tom and Grady.</i>

06:54.046 --> 06:56.537
<i>They were farmers,</i>
<i>just like my parents were.</i>

06:56.616 --> 07:00.052
<i>Simple people that cared about</i>
<i>their families and about each other.</i>

07:00.119 --> 07:03.987
<i>And yet somehow,</i>
<i>somewhere along the line,</i>
<i>time had passed them by,</i>

07:04.056 --> 07:08.254
<i>forgetting to tell them it was okay</i>
<i>to let go of the hatred and the anger.</i>

07:12.498 --> 07:14.466
Hi!
[ Kissing Sound ]

07:14.534 --> 07:17.002
Don't I get one of those?
Oh, I'm sorry, Daddy.

07:17.069 --> 07:20.561
I'm just so happy I could bust.
I love you.

07:20.640 --> 07:22.574
I'm sorry we kept
your husband out so late,

07:22.642 --> 07:24.974
but we had one hell
of a celebration.

07:25.044 --> 07:27.877
You're all just in time for breakfast.
Ada just made a fresh pot of coffee,

07:27.947 --> 07:30.108
and I made
Mama's strawberry shortcake.

07:30.183 --> 07:34.779
Mmm-mmm! This old man's
got to get to bed, honey.
I'll take a pass.

07:34.854 --> 07:38.051
Okay.
I'll see you later and see you
tomorrow night for supper. Clyde?

07:39.192 --> 07:41.422
<i>Yeah?</i>
Here's your robe, son.

07:43.062 --> 07:45.292
[ Engine Starts ]

07:55.708 --> 07:57.903
What's that for?
'Cause I love you.

07:57.977 --> 08:00.275
'Cause you're a wonderful daddy
and a terrific husband...

08:00.346 --> 08:03.543
and 'cause you love me enough
to join Daddy's huntin' club.

08:04.550 --> 08:07.314
Huntin' club?
<i>I know you didn't want to.</i>

08:07.386 --> 08:09.581
<i>I know you did it for me and Cody.</i>

08:11.257 --> 08:14.090
I love you for that.

08:14.160 --> 08:17.186
[ Kissing Sound ]
[ Laughs ]

08:17.263 --> 08:20.892
<i>Y'all keep on spooning like that out here,</i>
<i>and you won't want these treats.</i>

08:21.901 --> 08:24.062
Ah, come on now.
Dig in.

08:26.606 --> 08:28.597
Looks great.

08:30.076 --> 08:34.274
<i>Lord, Mr. Clyde,you eat your shortcake</i>
<i>just like my boy Nathaniel.</i>

08:34.347 --> 08:37.510
- They never do grow up, do they?
- No, they don't.

08:37.582 --> 08:39.573
You know, my mom
used to make the best-

08:39.652 --> 08:42.450
Clyde, your mama
couldn't boil water.

08:43.523 --> 08:46.356
Coffee. She used to make the best coffee
that would go great with this.

08:46.425 --> 08:52.227
<i>Oh, coffee. Or would you rather have</i>
<i>a large glass of cool milk</i>
<i>with Miss Lilly's shortcake?</i>

08:52.298 --> 08:54.858
He said he wanted coffee, Ada.

08:56.469 --> 08:59.461
Look, I'll go- I'll go get it.
No. No, you sit down.

08:59.539 --> 09:02.975
You let Ada fetch it.
Come on. Here you go.

09:03.042 --> 09:05.636
Mmm!
[ Laughs ]

09:11.684 --> 09:17.213
<i>Cody.! How many times has your father</i>
<i>told you not to point that at anyone?</i>

09:17.290 --> 09:19.224
[ Mumbles ]
<i>Come here, son.</i>

09:19.292 --> 09:21.283
Come on.
Give me the gun.

09:22.962 --> 09:25.988
It's all right.
Listen, I want you to sit down.
I wanna talk to you.

09:26.999 --> 09:31.333
When you get a little bit older,
I'll teach you how to shoot a gun, all right?

09:31.404 --> 09:36.842
But... you said you'd teach me
how to shoot today.

09:37.877 --> 09:41.438
Well, yeah, of course I did.
But I'm sure that I also must have said...

09:41.514 --> 09:44.176
